signature: RTree<T, S> delete(Entry<? extends T, ? extends S> entry, boolean all)

enhanced_by.method_name: add(Entry<? extends T, ? extends S> entry)
enhanced_by.reason: Both methods involve modifying the state of the RTree by adding or removing entries.
Both methods handle the deletion of entries, with the latter handling multiple entries.
The search method can be used to verify the absence of deleted entries, providing a way to assert the deletion operation.
The size method can be used to assert the reduction in the number of entries after deletion.
